            </div>
            <div class="building__desc">
              <div class="building__title">
                <div class="tag reverse">
                  <p>02 Building</p>
                </div>
                <h2>The Sunset Tower stands tall, bathed in the evening glow.</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="building__text">
                <p>The high-rise building illuminated by the setting sun offers a breathtaking view. Particularly captivating as the sun descends, the tall structure's glass windows and surfaces gleam beautifully in the evening light. During dusk, the surrounding scenery is bathed in deep orange and pink hues, resembling a picturesque painting. The reflection of the sunset's light on each floor of the building, as the sky turns orange, is truly mesmerizing and is sure to become a lifelong memory. Watching the sunset from the high vantage point of the building allows one to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life, quieting the mind and providing an opportunity to connect with the beauty of nature. Visitors can enjoy the view from this sunset-lit high-rise building and rejuvenate both body and soul.</p>
